---
title: Satay-Inspired Chicken Bowls with Peanuts and Sweet Chili Sauce
description: Sweet, spicy, crunchy and speedy! Skip the skewers for this satay-inspired chicken bowl. Marinate tender chicken with flavourful curry paste and Thai Seasoning while you prepare the rest of the meal. A quick sizzle under the broiler brings smoky grilled flavour that will keep you coming back for more!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/satay-inspired-chicken-bowls-5b95f8f9.jpg
